title.narrative: Communication and advocacy programmes are aligned to global and regional priorities

description.narrative: RO communication supported countries with strategies to lend a voice to the global and regional vision. A key result child placed at the centre of socio-political agenda in the region. Further, technical advisory support and oversight through both direct and remote means ensured that communication and public advocacy programmes are aligned to both the global and regional vision. Tactics such as the use of high-level events for leaders, social media engagement, capacity strengthening & media engagement and support of campaigns, both global and regional priorities were positioned. Consequently, there was more political salience, earned media, public engagement and support. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:05/02/2020
